longBusinessSummary: Heliospectra AB (publ) provides light control systems and related services for greenhouse and controlled plant growth environments worldwide. It offers MITRA, a modular solution for indoor and greenhouse; Elixia luminaires; Siera, a vertical farming solution for predictable and repeatable results; and DYNA, a programmable LED plant lighting system. The company also offers helioCARE services comprising light planning, on site, trials, and cultivation training services. Heliospectra AB (publ) was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Gothenburg, Sweden.
